Berapa pun nilai wakaf Anda, sangat berarti bagi keberlangsungan program ini.",1,"src/content/faq/1-dicicil.md","70f1aec74710873d",{"html":20,"metadata":21},"",{"headings":22,"localImagePaths":23,"remoteImagePaths":24,"frontmatter":25,"imagePaths":26},[],[],[],{"question":14,"answer":15,"order":16},[],"2-laporan",{"id":27,"data":29,"filePath":33,"digest":34,"rendered":35},{"question":30,"answer":31,"order":32},"Apakah saya akan mendapat laporan penggunaan dana?","Ya, kami memberikan laporan berkala melalui update di website dan media sosial. Setiap perkembangan pembangunan akan didokumentasikan dan dibagikan kepada seluruh wakif. Anda juga bisa langsung bertanya melalui WhatsApp kami.",2,"src/content/faq/2-laporan.md","c8ce3c712ddc33ab",{"html":20,"metadata":36},{"headings":37,"localImagePaths":38,"remoteImagePaths":39,"frontmatter":40,"imagePaths":41},[],[],[],{"question":30,"answer":31,"order":32},[],"3-transparansi",{"id":42,"data":44,"filePath":48,"digest":49,"rendered":50},{"question":45,"answer":46,"order":47},"Bagaimana transparansi pengelolaan dana wakaf?","Pengelolaan dana dilakukan secara transparan melalui Yayasan Khoiru Ummah Indonesia Madani yang terdaftar di Kemenkumham. Seluruh penggunaan dana didokumentasikan dan dapat diakses oleh wakif. Kami juga rutin memposting update progress di media sosial.",3,"src/content/faq/3-transparansi.md","72271d73225e5b54",{"html":20,"metadata":51},{"headings":52,"localImagePaths":53,"remoteImagePaths":54,"frontmatter":55,"imagePaths":56},[],[],[],{"question":45,"answer":46,"order":47},[],"4-legalitas",{"id":57,"data":59,"filePath":63,"digest":64,"rendered":65},{"question":60,"answer":61,"order":62},"Apakah legalitas yayasan sudah terjamin?","Ya, yayasan kami telah terdaftar di Kemenkumham RI dengan SK AHU-0010190.AH.01.04.Tahun 2018 dan memiliki NPWP yayasan yang aktif. Anda bisa memverifikasi langsung melalui situs resmi Kemenkumham RI.",4,"src/content/faq/4-legalitas.md","d0b9cc5d7cbc26b0",{"html":20,"metadata":66},{"headings":67,"localImagePaths":68,"remoteImagePaths":69,"frontmatter":70,"imagePaths":71},[],[],[],{"question":60,"answer":61,"order":62},[],"5-program",{"id":72,"data":74,"filePath":78,"digest":79,"rendered":80},{"question":75,"answer":76,"order":77},"Apa saja program yang dibangun di Villa Tahfizh?","Villa Tahfizh akan menjadi pusat pendidikan tahfiz Al-Qur'an yang dilengkapi dengan fasilitas asrama, ruang belajar, musholla, dan sarana pendukung lainnya untuk para penghafal Al-Qur'an. Dana sebesar Rp 13 Miliar sudah mencakup pembangunan dan sarana prasarana.",5,"src/content/faq/5-program.md","cf437cf1909f21d8",{"html":20,"metadata":81},{"headings":82,"localImagePaths":83,"remoteImagePaths":84,"frontmatter":85,"imagePaths":86},[],[],[],{"question":75,"answer":76,"order":77},[],"testimoni",["Map",89,90,104,105],"1-ahmad",{"id":89,"data":91,"filePath":95,"digest":96,"rendered":97},{"name":92,"role":93,"quote":94,"rating":77},"Ahmad Fauzi","Wakif dari Jakarta","Alhamdulillah bisa ikut ambil bagian dalam wakaf untuk pembangunan Villa Tahfizh. Semoga menjadi ladang pahala jariyah yang terus mengalir.","src/content/testimoni/1-ahmad.md","305022f7bfb26cc7",{"html":20,"metadata":98},{"headings":99,"localImagePaths":100,"remoteImagePaths":101,"frontmatter":102,"imagePaths":103},[],[],[],{"name":92,"role":93,"quote":94,"rating":77},[],"2-siti",{"id":104,"data":106,"filePath":110,"digest":111,"rendered":112},{"name":107,"role":108,"quote":109,"rating":77},"Siti Nurhaliza","Wakif dari Bandung","Transparansi laporannya sangat baik. Setiap progress selalu diupdate. Senang bisa berkontribusi untuk rumah para penghafal Al-Qur'an.","src/content/testimoni/2-siti.md","0d51c11a78aed97b",{"html":20,"metadata":113},{"headings":114,"localImagePaths":115,"remoteImagePaths":116,"frontmatter":117,"imagePaths":118},[],[],[],{"name":107,"role":108,"quote":109,"rating":77},[],"updates",["Map",121,122,139,140],"2026-02-15-survey",{"id":121,"data":123,"body":127,"filePath":128,"digest":129,"re